After careful consideration and consultation with the incoming StoryTeller, we will not be changing the system which we came up with for the functioning of status.  Also, as entertaining as it could possibly be, negative traits would definitly be too big a can of worms.<br>
I'm posting this in a separate post, so that people can compare the changes -Marisa]<br>
(( OOC: A few people lost / resigned from positions due to the 3-week absence rule, or stepping down.  Raven on the Bloodhunted list was taken out by Prophet, earning him a second Loyal status trait.  K'lith was taken out by The Herald, on the Bloodhunted list from long, long ago, earning him the Esteemed status trait.  Clarification was made to Clan Tremere, the CLAN is not Banished, the Clan was asked to leave so as to limit the threat they have posed to the Populace of Santa Carla.  Only Eric was Banished.  This was for their own safety as a Clan as well as the City's safety, a double-edged diplomatic, if risky, move to prevent whole-scale bloodshed.  Negative status traits would be a big can of worms, but oh so fun.  Perhaps another time. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->     -- Kirstin))<br>
